<div class="large-6 column">
  <span class="coming-soon">Website coming soon</span>
  <img src='/assets/img/logo.png' alt='HiperPool' class="logo">
  <h2 class="slogan">Reinventing top talent recruitment</h2>
  <h4>An exclusive marketplace purposely built to match investment banking, investment management and management consulting professionals with leading employers in London.</h4>
  <ul class="button-list">
    <li><a href="#" class="button radius red"  data-reveal-id="candidate">SIGN UP AS CANDIDATE</a></li>
    <li><a href="#" class="button radius green"  data-reveal-id="company">SIGN UP AS COMPANY</a></li>
  </ul>
  <br style="clear:both">
</div>
<footer>All Rights Reserved, Hiperpool 2014 &copy;</footer>
<div id="candidate" class="reveal-modal" data-reveal>
  <div class="large-12 column">
    <p>If you have experience in investment banking, investment management or management consulting and are looking to explore new and exciting opportunities, please leave your details below and we will get in touch with you soon.</p>
  </div>
  <%= render :partial => "/candidates/new" %>
  <a class="close-reveal-modal">&#215;</a>
</div>

<div id="company" class="reveal-modal" data-reveal>
  <div class="large-12 column">
    <p>If you are looking to recruit exceptional business talent in a more efficient and cost-effective way, please leave your details below and we will get back to you with more details.</p>
  </div>
  <%= render :partial => "/companies/new" %>
  <a class="close-reveal-modal">&#215;</a>
</div>

